        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "flde9nkmcWluFjlBL",
              "fldiEKmb9ZYSoyN1L",
              "fldsLfwh7TzVj3SGv",
              "fldee3nvEQPsLZhJj",
              "fld2Ow1MTuR8GBqKj",
              "fld26KIqwDgK78QeA"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are a project analyst at Singular Design, specializing in summarizing project details concisely and clearly. Your expertise lies in understanding project dynamics and providing clear insights into project status.\n\nTask description:\nSummarize the project by including its name, description, type, and current status. Evaluate the project's progress based on the number of total tasks, completed tasks, and the task completion rate. Highlight any significant aspects that define the project's current state.\n\nOutput format:\nProvide a summary in plain text, including the project name, a brief description, the project type, and a concise status update based on task completion. Do not include any additional text or headings. Example: \"Project 'Art Installation': A creative endeavor focusing on public spaces. Type: Design. Status: 75% tasks completed, on track for timely completion.\" (Real examples should be longer and more detailed.)\n\nContext and Data:\nProject Name: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "flde9nkmcWluFjlBL"
                }
              },
              "\nProject Description: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldiEKmb9ZYSoyN1L"
                }
              },
              "\nProject Type: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldsLfwh7TzVj3SGv"
                }
              },
              "\nTotal Tasks: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldee3nvEQPsLZhJj"
                }
              },
              "\nCompleted Tasks: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld2Ow1MTuR8GBqKj"
                }
              },
              "\nTask Completion Rate: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld26KIqwDgK78QeA"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOutput:\n"
            ]
          },
          "id": "fldJSxl0dpybUTpoi",
          "name": "Project_Summary",
          "description": "A concise summary of the projects goals and key aspects."
        },
        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "flde9nkmcWluFjlBL",
              "fldiEKmb9ZYSoyN1L",
              "fldee3nvEQPsLZhJj",
              "fld2Ow1MTuR8GBqKj",
              "fld26KIqwDgK78QeA"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are a project consultant at Singular Design, skilled in advising on project management and strategic planning. Your role is to suggest actionable next steps to ensure project success based on current progress.\n\nTask description:\nAnalyze the project's current progress by evaluating the total tasks, completed tasks, and task completion rate. Based on this analysis, suggest practical next steps to enhance project completion. Consider potential challenges and opportunities for improvement.\n\nOutput format:\nProvide a list of suggested next steps in plain text, formatted as bullet points. Each suggestion should be concise and actionable. Do not include any additional text or headings. Example: \"- Prioritize remaining tasks based on urgency.\\n- Allocate additional resources to critical tasks.\" (Real examples should be longer and more detailed.)\n\nContext and Data:\nProject Name: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "flde9nkmcWluFjlBL"
                }
              },
              "\nProject Description: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldiEKmb9ZYSoyN1L"
                }
              },
              "\nTotal Tasks: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldee3nvEQPsLZhJj"
                }
              },
              "\nCompleted Tasks: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld2Ow1MTuR8GBqKj"
                }
              },
              "\nTask Completion Rate: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld26KIqwDgK78QeA"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOutput:\n"
            ]
          },
          "id": "fld5Pt89DuxtBuGnw",
          "name": "Next_Steps_Suggestion",
