              "fldKhmBmjYztWb3WM",
              "fldpRhywbXeOwGTom",
              "fldl7tb6AzIpadPAx"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are a project manager at Singular Design, specializing in summarizing task details for quick review. Your role is to provide concise and clear summaries that capture the essence of the task, suitable for a design industry context.\n\nTask description:\nAnalyze the provided task information to create a brief summary. Focus on highlighting the task name, its current status, progress, and the due date. Ensure the summary is easy to understand and provides a quick overview of the task's key aspects.\n\nOutput format:\nProvide a summary in plain text, containing the task name, status, progress percentage, and due date. Do not include any additional text or headings. Format the output as follows: \"[Task Name]: [Status], [Progress]% complete, due on [Due Date].\" If any information is missing, state \"Information incomplete.\"\n\nContext and Data:\nTask Name: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "flduEmnjgAw7iJFqy"
                }
              },
              "\nTask Description: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldoUNx1gs2uLVY1Z"
                }
              },
              "\nStatus: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldKhmBmjYztWb3WM"
                }
              },
              "\nProgress: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldpRhywbXeOwGTom"
                }
              },
              "\nDue Date: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldl7tb6AzIpadPAx"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOutput:\n"
            ]
          },
          "id": "fldGTDqnbooGmJTRw",
          "name": "Task_Summary",
          "description": "A brief description of the tasks purpose and key details."
        },
        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fldKhmBmjYztWb3WM",
              "fld28DGOfpcY5sRtY",
              "fldpRhywbXeOwGTom"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "Assume the role of a task consultant at Singular Design, providing actionable recommendations for project tasks. You are skilled in analyzing task status and project complexities to suggest the next best action.\n\nTask description:\nEvaluate the task's current status, progress, and the complexity level of the related project type. Based on this analysis, recommend a practical next step that aligns with the task's needs and project type. Consider whether the task is blocked, in progress, or nearing completion, and suggest actions accordingly.\n\nOutput format:\nOutput a single, clear recommendation in plain text. Do not include any additional text or explanations. Format the output as follows: \"Next step: [Recommended Action].\" If unable to determine a recommendation, state \"Recommendation unavailable.\"\n\nContext and Data:\nStatus: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldKhmBmjYztWb3WM"
                }
              },
              "\nProject Type Complexity: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld28DGOfpcY5sRtY"
                }
              },
              "\nProgress: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldpRhywbXeOwGTom"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOutput:\n"
            ]
          },
          "id": "fldhyQN8BdjygDHiu",
          "name": "Next_Action_Recommendation",
          "description": "Recommended next steps for a task/project. Stores text descriptions."
        }
